Resources.Source: Creating the cache directory failed and then the invalid cache folder and/or lock file could not be removed.
Resources.Translation: Ustvarjanje imenika predpomnilnika ni uspelo in neveljavne mape predpomnilnika in / ali datoteke zaklepanja ni bilo možno odstraniti.

Resources.Source: Could not get a lock on the file within the allowed tries.
Resources.Translation: V dovoljenih poskusih datoteke ni bilo možno zakleniti.

Resources.Source: Could not write to lock file of cache directory.
Resources.Translation: Ni možno pisati v datoteko zaklepanja imenika predpomnilnika.

Resources.Source: The requested file was not found.
Resources.Translation: Zahtevane datoteke ni bilo mogoče najti.

Resources.Source: Locking the cache directory failed and then the invalid cache folder and/or lock file could not be removed.
Resources.Translation: Zaklepanje imenika predpomnilnika ni uspelo in neveljavne mape predpomnilnika in / ali datoteke zaklepanja ni bilo možno odstraniti.

Resources.Source: The version {0} of file {1} does not exist.
The package cache directory is not accessible. It may not exist or you may not have access to it.
Resources.Translation: Imenik predpomnilnika paketa ni dostopen. Morda ne obstaja ali nimate dostopa do njega.

Resources.Source: '{0}' does not have the correct format.
The package is not valid and cannot be read. More information: {0}
Resources.Translation: Paket ni veljaven in ga ni možno prebrati. Več informacij: {0}
